          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Highly enriched Zn-64 target (99.4%) in form of discs",
                "were used.",
                "Titanium monitor foils of 30+-1 mum thickness were",
                "used to determine the integrated ion beam current on",
                "the stacked-foil target .",
                "A stack of five Zn-64 foils together with three Ti",
                "monitor foils was prepared.",
                "In order to avoid any losses of activity by recoil",
                "processes, each foil was enveloped by a catcher foil",
                "of pure Al of 22.5+-1 mum thickness."
              ]
            }
          ],
